01:04.120 --> 01:05.010
I'm on my break.

01:05.030 --> 01:06.370
What are you talking about a break?

01:06.390 --> 01:08.660
You're not working at the mall,there is no break.

01:08.680 --> 01:10.780
I'm on my break,man.

01:11.380 --> 01:13.450
Listen,there are laws,okay?

01:13.490 --> 01:15.740
Well,it's one of your regulars.

01:15.760 --> 01:17.920
You want me to put it through to someone else,I will.

01:17.950 --> 01:20.480
Hit me,baby,one more time.

01:21.770 --> 01:24.720
Hello,and thank you for calling PSYLINE.

01:24.750 --> 01:26.670
Your personal phone psychic is on

01:26.690 --> 01:30.650
and ready to open the portals to the psychic universe.

01:30.710 --> 01:32.650
Michael,is that you?

01:32.670 --> 01:34.400
Thank God. It's Tanya King.

01:34.430 --> 01:37.400
Ms. King!How was Paris?

01:37.510 --> 01:39.180
Oh,Michael...

01:39.210 --> 01:41.950
Michael,Michael,Michael.

01:41.970 --> 01:44.270
Ms. King,you can call me crazy

01:44.290 --> 01:46.520
but I'm sensing some bad energy here.

01:46.530 --> 01:48.050
Has something happened?

01:48.070 --> 01:50.200
It's... it's Gregory.

01:50.230 --> 01:51.800
I've lost him.

01:51.900 --> 01:52.830
You're kidding!

01:52.850 --> 01:54.350
Thought he was kind of big for that.

01:54.370 --> 01:56.340
He's dead,Michael.

01:56.360 --> 01:58.400
He's been murdered.

01:59.580 --> 02:01.600
Oh,Michael.

02:01.620 --> 02:03.700
Well,that's not good.

02:14.780 --> 02:15.950
Hello.

02:15.970 --> 02:18.800
Hey,it's me.Sorry to wake you,but I got a problem.

02:18.900 --> 02:20.200
Maybe you could walk me through it.

02:20.220 --> 02:21.980
Well,I'll try.What's going on?

02:22.000 --> 02:24.110
I'm here at a crime scene--robbery gone bad.

02:24.130 --> 02:25.910
Man of the house surprised an intruder.

02:25.930 --> 02:28.000
Got his head bashed in for his trouble.

02:28.120 --> 02:29.740
Wife comes home from a trip to Paris

02:29.760 --> 02:31.970
and finds him dead in the living room.

02:33.230 --> 02:35.070
Did you say Paris?

02:35.090 --> 02:36.140
Yeah,but that's not important.

02:36.160 --> 02:37.630
Here's where I need your help.

02:37.650 --> 02:38.800
She locked herself in her bedroom.

02:38.820 --> 02:42.040
Apparently she's talking on the phone with her own personal psychic.

02:42.720 --> 02:43.830
What do you think?

02:43.850 --> 02:47.380
I think I'm... on my way over.

